}

# v1.8: midlang.glass is a Glass-in-Glass interpreter for a small
# expression language WITH CLOSURES AND RECURSION (let-rec). prism.glass
# reads it from disk, compiles it through its own pipeline, and runs it.
# The midlang program computes factorial(5) via let-rec, returning
# (MInt(120), MInt(30)) — the factorial result and a curried-add result.
