# v4.47: refined-param lambdas. The parser now accepts `where (pred)`
# after a lambda's typed param; eval wraps the resulting closure in a
# VRefinedClos so the predicate fires on every application. Positive
# case returns the body's result; negative case surfaces the standard
# "refinement violated at runtime" message through the demo loop.
